show.description: A runaway groom and a jilted bride cross paths in a twist of fate, sparking an unexpected marriage built on secrets and misunderstandings. As their worlds collide—his wealthy identity hidden and her pride wounded—they navigate love, deception, and redemption in this romantic drama.
